    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>初识android 实现两个页面的跳转以及数据的交互</p>
<p>下面是我的工程结构 <img src="/img/context/android-activity1.png" title="application" alt="application"></p>
<h2 id="页面的跳转">页面的跳转</h2>
<p>首先在layout内新建一个aty1.xml 在java内新建一个Aty1类</p>
<figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">public <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Aty1</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">Activity</span></span>&#123;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">protected</span> void onCreate(<span class="type">Bundle</span> savedInstanceState) &#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);</div><div class="line">        setContentView(<span class="type">R</span>.layout.aty1);</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在activity_main.xml中添加一个Button 修改Button 的id为bthStartAty1 <figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;Button</div><div class="line">    android:<span class="built_in">text</span>=<span class="string">"Start Aty1"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_width=<span class="string">"wrap_content"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_height=<span class="string">"wrap_content"</span></div><div class="line">    android:<span class="built_in">id</span>=<span class="string">"@+id/btnStartAty1"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_below=<span class="string">"@+id/tvOut"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_alignParentLeft=<span class="string">"true"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_alignParentStart=<span class="string">"true"</span></div><div class="line">    android:layout_marginTop=<span class="string">"10dp"</span> /&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在MainActivity类中 <figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">public <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MainActivity</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">AppCompatActivity</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">Button</span> btnStartAty1;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">TextView</span> tvOut;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> void onCreate(<span class="type">Bundle</span> savedInstanceState) &#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);</div><div class="line">        setContentView(<span class="type">R</span>.layout.activity_main);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        btnStartAty1 = (<span class="type">Button</span>) findViewById(<span class="type">R</span>.id.btnStartAty1);</div><div class="line">        btnStartAty1.setOnClickListener(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">View</span>.<span class="type">OnClickListener</span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">            public void onClick(<span class="type">View</span> view) &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                <span class="type">Intent</span> i = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">Intent</span>(<span class="type">MainActivity</span>.<span class="keyword">this</span>,<span class="type">Aty1</span>.<span class="keyword">class</span>);</div><div class="line">                startActivity(i);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    &#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>打开模拟器，点击MainActivity中的Button就可以跳转到Aty1</p>
<h2 id="从mainactivity传递数据到aty1">从MainActivity传递数据到Aty1</h2>
<p>在MainActivty类中的按钮监听其中添加</p>
<figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">btnStartAty1.setOnClickListener(<span class="keyword">new</span> View.OnClickListener() &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onClick</span><span class="params">(View view)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                Intent i = <span class="keyword">new</span> Intent(MainActivity.<span class="keyword">this</span>,Aty1.class);</div><div class="line">                <span class="comment">//i.putExtra("txt","Hello ATY");</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                Bundle data = <span class="keyword">new</span> Bundle();</div><div class="line">                data.putString(<span class="string">"text"</span>,<span class="string">"Hello Aty1"</span>);</div><div class="line">                i.putExtras(data);</div><div class="line">                startActivity(i);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                </div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 aty1.xml中添加Textview,修改id 为tvOut 在Aty1类中定义一个Textview <figure class="highlight abnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">private TextView tvOut<span class="comment">;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在create方法中添加 <figure class="highlight abnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">tvOut</span> = (TextView) findViewById(R.id.tvOut)<span class="comment">;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Bundle data = getIntent().getExtras()<span class="comment">;</span></div><div class="line">String txt = data.getString(<span class="string">"text"</span>)<span class="comment">;</span></div><div class="line">tvOut.setText(txt)<span class="comment">;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这样当点击MainActivity中的按钮时 Aty1就接受了从MainActivity传递的“Hello Aty1”显示在TextView中</p>
<p>在Aty1中添加一个关闭按钮，在类中添加监听器 <figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">btnClose.setOnClickListener(<span class="keyword">new</span> View.OnClickListener() &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onClick</span><span class="params">(View view)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">                </div><div class="line">                finish();</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>当点击该Button时会关闭Aty1</p>
<h2 id="在mainactivity中接受aty1返回的数据">在MainActivity中接受Aty1返回的数据</h2>
<p>在Aty1 button监听器中添加 <figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">btnClose.setOnClickListener(<span class="keyword">new</span> View.OnClickListener() &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onClick</span><span class="params">(View view)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">                Intent i = <span class="keyword">new</span> Intent();</div><div class="line">                i.putExtra(<span class="string">"result"</span>,<span class="string">"hello mainActivity"</span>);</div><div class="line">                setResult(<span class="number">0</span>,i);</div><div class="line">                finish();</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在MainActivity中 定义一个TextView tvOut</p>
<p>重写onActivityResult <figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"> <span class="meta">@Override</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onActivityResult</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> requestCode, <span class="keyword">int</span> resultCode, Intent data)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        String result = data.getStringExtra(<span class="string">"result"</span>);</div><div class="line">        tvOut.setText(result);</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">super</span>.onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>将按钮监听器中的startActitvity(i)改为startActitvityForResult(i,0)</p>
<p>这样当在Aty1中点击按钮后，MainActivity就会接受到数据并显示在TextView中</p>]]></content>
    
